A User can not Share a Post from another User if he/she is Blocked by that User
A User can not Share a Post from a Community if he/she is Blocked by that Community
If a User is Deleted all his/her Shared items are UnShared
A User receives a Notification if his/her post is Shared by another User
A User can Share a Post from a Community on his/her Wall
A Post Shared will be put in the User that is sharing his/her Wall
A Post Shared will be put in the Wall of the Followers of the User that is sharing
A User receives a Notification if a Post is Shared by another User on his Wall
A Post Shared will appear on a User's Wall
